::Prowl::

Prowl takes in a near-trembling breath as Iron Raptor's breath touches his 
neck. He smiles, suddenly feeling very excited.

"One quiet place coming right up," he says, opening his wings. He tightens 
his hold on Iron Raptor and launches himself into the air.

Prowl turns his head and looks at Iron Raptor, another wave of emotion 
passing through him as he kisses her again.
